CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 29, 1962, pg. 5 reads: "Two Years Old - Sylvia Ann Porter celebrated her second birthday recently at a party at the home of her parents. The pretty little miss is the daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Fred Pryor Jr. of Homewood. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Sylvia Ann Porter wearing dark plaid pinafore dress, seated in home of parents Mr. and Mrs. Fred Pryor Jr., Homewood
